  <div id="contact">follow me on <a href="http://www.twitter.com/MarcusEMcDuffie">Twitter</a> or check me out on <a href="http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1044309214">Facebook</a>.</div>
</header>
<p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
